==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Lambskin
<hw>Lamb"skin`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
skin of a lamb; especially, a skin dressed with the wool on, and used as
a mat. Also used adjectively.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A kind of woolen.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lambskinnet</ent>⟦br⟧
